    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Astromine》是一款支持合作的生存游戏，背景设定在一个完全可破坏的体素星系中。</strong><br>每一颗行星、生物与建筑都由具有真实物理属性的体素构成。挖穿星球、推倒墙体、点燃基地、剖开外星怪物——一切都在真实物理下发生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/640cc8f957ba0c7702c5caeb26a7ff85.poster.avif?t=1772028437\" width=1170 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/640cc8f957ba0c7702c5caeb26a7ff85.webm?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/640cc8f957ba0c7702c5caeb26a7ff85.mp4?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>程序化体素行星</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >降落在完全可破坏、程序生成的行星上——每颗都是拥有独特地形、资源与危险的球形世界。<br>穿透外星地壳、一路挖入行星核心，掠夺你在生存与扩张中所需的原材料。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实物理生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种材料都拥有真实的物理特性。<br>木材会燃烧并在受压时坍塌，金属能支撑高耸结构，电力则驱动庞大的网络系统。<br>火势会蔓延，基地会因地基薄弱而崩塌——在这里，想要活下去不仅靠搜刮，更靠工程学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/d424ec2adb011c96bb72e8d52fa47518.poster.avif?t=1772028437\" width=1170 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/d424ec2adb011c96bb72e8d52fa47518.webm?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/d424ec2adb011c96bb72e8d52fa47518.mp4?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>机器人之间的战争</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一台为争夺星系而战的机器。<br>敌对机器人阵营在各个外星世界上建立了重兵把守的基地。<br>每个前哨都是一场关于规划与破坏的挑战：逐体素突破墙体、切断电力系统、一步步拆毁敌方防御。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有生命的外星世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外星生命同样由体素构成。<br>撕开血肉与装甲，切入敌人体内寻找弱点，看着你的武器在物理效果下将它们一块块拆解。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造、扩张、征服</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从生存避难所到轨道要塞，使用具有真实物理的体素材料建造你的基地与星舰。<br>驾驶飞船在行星之间航行，扩张你的势力范围，为掌控整个星系而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/568dd5a9d2934551666bd19da39fe043.poster.avif?t=1772028437\" width=1170 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/568dd5a9d2934551666bd19da39fe043.webm?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833210/extras/568dd5a9d2934551666bd19da39fe043.mp4?t=1772028437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
